# Personal / AI-generated artifacts. These reflect your CV, applications,
# and the LLM's per-job verdicts — they should NOT be committed on a public
# fork. The repo ships `*.example.*` templates as a starting point; copy
# them to the canonical paths below or run `pnpm run setup-brief` and the
# scripted/UI flows will populate the real files locally.
config/candidate-brief.md
config/applied.json
config/preferences.json
config/cv.pdf
config/cv.docx
config/cv.md
config/cv.txt
